Two different calibrated lamps were used to determine the IRF across the spectral range from 245‚Äì853¬†nm. For the violet, green, orange, and red spectral ranges of the transmission and VIO reflection spectrometers, a¬†calibrated Labsphere integrating sphere and lamp assembly was used. This lamp provided uniform radiance generally at the 2% level or better across its aperture (‚àº100mm\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
