				\usepackage{mathrsfs}
				\usepackage{upgreek}
				\setlength{\oddsidemargin}{-69pt}
				\begin{document}$\sim715\text{--}853~\text{nm}$\end{document}) used a reduced set of 70 rows for integration. This trade accepts slightly lower IRF for better optical resolution in this region.

